Refers to the code for each cedent investment classification. This is Classification of cedent investment in SPV i.e. for Group purposes. Options are
Option 1. No investment held in SPV. SPV authorized in accordance with L1 art 211 or equivalent regulation i.e. refer E1 above.
Option 2. SPV non regulated entity or does not comply with L1 art 211 or equivalent regulation i.e. refer E1 above.
Option 3. SPV is considered to be intra group where a participating undertaking of a Group hold notes of an SPV.
